text: Pizza is really good and freshly prepared, we got a regular crust and a stuffed pizza and unfortunately I feel like the stuffed pizza is missing something? Maybe needs more cheese inside? Just tastes a little off balance with the amount of …More

name: Ray Kirby
text: The food is always great and excellent service, the staff is always very attentive and nice.  Highly recommended the Mediterranean pizza in thin crust, take it home and cook whenever you're ready.  The salad and pizza for $20 is a deal.  Also, veteran owned.

name: LaNae Yates
text: I absolutely love the idea of taking home a fresh made pizza and baking it when I’m ready. I decided to try the spinach and artichoke chicken pizza and I was not disappointed. We have a family tradition of getting heart shaped pizza for …More

name: kaledev
text: It was good in terms of taste, but I'm fairly certain the person made it wrong... There was literally three times as much cheese as you would see on a standard pizza. So much that when I baked it the top slid off. I'm sure the guy just screwed up, but I had wide eyes as he was throwing a years supply of cheese on there.

name: S. Hinson
text: Pizza is ALWAYS consistently good, and the staff is ALWAYS friendly!

name: Greg Crook
text: Absolutely fantastic!!  I love the fact I can eat it when "I" want to, right out of the oven. The fact they use all fresh ingredients makes a clear difference in how I feel the next day. Being a bit of a health freak, I don't have the bloating etc that usually comes from eating the other typical pizza joints.
